Single Cell QFeatures data

Source: R/data.R
scp1.Rd

A small QFeatures object with SCoPE2 data. The object is composed of 5 assays, including 3 PSM-level assays, 1 peptide assay and 1 protein assay.

scp1

Format

An object of class QFeatures of length 5.

Examples

data(scp1)
scp1
#> An instance of class QFeatures containing 5 assays:
#>  [1] 190321S_LCA10_X_FP97AG: SingleCellExperiment with 195 rows and 11 columns 
#>  [2] 190222S_LCA9_X_FP94BM: SingleCellExperiment with 187 rows and 11 columns 
#>  [3] 190914S_LCB3_X_16plex_Set_21: SingleCellExperiment with 160 rows and 16 columns 
#>  [4] peptides: SingleCellExperiment with 522 rows and 38 columns 
#>  [5] proteins: SingleCellExperiment with 296 rows and 38 columns
